1. *Lari* je danas otišao na sastanak. (Larry went to a meeting today.)
2. Danas sam video *Larija* kako trči po parku. (Today I saw Larry running in the park.)
3. *Lariev* posao je veoma stresan. (Larry's job is very stressful.)
4. *Lariju* je potrebna pomoć oko ovog zadatka. (Larry needs help with this task.)
5. *Larieve* ideje su uvek inovativne. (Larry's ideas are always innovative.)

Note: In Serbian, the name Larry is typically spelled "Lari." However, depending on the case and gender of the sentence, the spelling may change to "Larija" or "Lariev."